data.description:
The Indiana floor plan. Wonderful open floor plan, Living room with high ceilings open to dining area and kitchen. Beautiful kitchen with granite counter tops and tile back splash, stainless steel appliances, large island, and rich wood cabinets with crown molding and hidden hinges. Four bedrooms with two 3/4 and one half bath. Great features like refrigerated air, tile flooring in living areas, carpeting in bedrooms, and shingle roof. . This home is currently under construction please visit Model Home at 7600 Dawnlight Ln., El Paso, TX 79911. Open Sun-Fri 11am -6pm and Sat 10a,-6pm
Photos are for demonstration purposes only not of actual home.
